7.4,, 102,, Animation, Action, Adventure, Drama,, Peter Chung, Andy Jones,, Akio Ohtsuka, Clayton Watson, Pamela Adlon, Hedy Burress,, The Animatrix is a collection of several animated short films, detailing the backstory of the &#x22;Matrix&#x22; universe, and the original war between man and machines which led to the creation of the Matrix.